35
00:01:53,660 --> 00:01:55,540
So I just walk around the street to see.

36
00:01:56,180 --> 00:01:57,380
You can also do business?

37
00:01:58,060 --> 00:01:59,000
We're new here

38
00:01:59,024 --> 00:02:00,436
