39
00:02:01,060 --> 00:02:02,100
My brother asked me

40
00:02:02,100 --> 00:02:03,440
not to worry about the livelihood.

41
00:02:03,540 --> 00:02:05,180
But I don't want to sit back and enjoy it.

42
00:02:05,620 --> 00:02:07,020
You are a person of integrity.

43
00:02:07,540 --> 00:02:08,860
I must honestly inform you

44
00:02:09,700 --> 00:02:11,300
the competition in the capital is fierce.

45
00:02:11,660 --> 00:02:12,700
If you rashly barge in,

46
00:02:12,700 --> 00:02:13,800
it might be hard to sustain.

47
00:02:16,020 --> 00:02:16,860
Moreover,

48
00:02:16,980 --> 00:02:18,660
