is better than wasting time in hesitation.

54
00:02:27,020 --> 00:02:27,860
What do you think?

55
00:02:29,380 --> 00:02:30,980
Since you have such determination,

56
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:32,560
I will do my utmost to support you.

57
00:02:33,660 --> 00:02:34,620
Thank you, Mr. Song.

58
00:02:38,460 --> 00:02:40,140
It's almost noon.

59
00:02:41,060 --> 00:02:41,900
First of all,

60
00:02:42,580 --> 00:02:44,340
let me treat you to the most exquisite snacks

61
00:02:44,340 --> 00:02:45,180
in the capital.

62
00:02:45,180 --> 00:02:48,820
(Yizhan Liunian)

63
00:02:56,660 --> 00:02:58,380
With delicate hands, she kneads the dough,

64
00:02:58,460 --> 00:03:00,280
frying it in oil to produce a tender yellow.

65
00:03:00,340 --> 00:03:01,480
This refers to the ring cake.

66
00:03:02,140 --> 00:03:03,340
Please have a taste.

67
00:03:15,980 --> 00:03:16,980
This is really delicious.

68
00:03:19,060 --> 00:03:19,900
By the way,

69
00:03:20,340 --> 00:03:21,980
in your opinion,

70
00:03:22,300 --> 00:03:24,460
