71
00:03:24,860 --> 00:03:25,700
Making money?

72
00:03:27,300 --> 00:03:29,140
I have little research on business.

73
00:03:29,700 --> 00:03:30,940
However, as for my family,

74
00:03:31,100 --> 00:03:32,680
my mother's money is the easiest to earn.

75
00:03:33,500 --> 00:03:35,420
