76
00:03:35,420 --> 00:03:36,784
and the makeup on the face

77
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,110
all need to be bought in batches.

78
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:40,090
And that rouge comes in different colors.

79
00:03:40,300 --> 00:03:41,990
In my opinion, there isn't much difference.

80
00:03:42,100 --> 00:03:43,700
In her view, it's totally different.

81
00:03:44,740 --> 00:03:45,580
She never thought

82
00:03:45,580 --> 00:03:46,860
there's too much jewelry.

83
00:03:47,420 --> 00:03:48,660
What she wants to wear

84
00:03:48,660 --> 00:03:50,100
must be the one she doesn't have.

85
00:03:51,300 --> 00:03:52,500
Actually, I think

86
00:03:52,940 --> 00:03:54,720
a woman's nature of loving beauty

87
00:03:54,744 --> 00:03:55,756
is truly adorable.

88
00:03:56,180 --> 00:03:57,500
Even though the jewelry

89
00:03:58,060 --> 00:03:59,580
is cheap and unattractive,

90
00:03:59,580 --> 00:04:00,820
many people still buy it.

91
00:04:01,260 --> 00:04:02,860
Your words remind me.

92
00:04:03,300 --> 00:04:05,300
Maybe I can start from this aspect.

93
00:04:05,530 --> 00:04:06,380
There's no rush.

94
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:07,430
Think about it carefully.

95
00:04:07,890 --> 00:04:08,740
Greasy?

96
00:04:08,860 --> 00:04:09,700
Not at all.

97
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,000
Serve tea.

98
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:12,860
Coming.

99
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:19,900
Wow!

100
00:04:41,100 --> 00:04:42,100
Please enjoy your time.

101
00:04:42,500 --> 00:04:43,340
Thank you.

102
00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:45,460
Really impressive!

103
00:04:46,260 --> 00:04:47,620
In the capital,

104
00:04:48,140 --> 00:04:50,780
even drinking tea is so unique.

105
00:04:52,700 --> 00:04:54,220
If one has no skills,

106
00:04:54,380 --> 00:04:55,740
it's indeed hard to settle down in.

107
00:04:56,620 --> 00:04:58,980
Business is business and life is life.

108
00:05:00,300 --> 00:05:02,380
Right now, don't waste her skill

109
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:03,940
and the essence of heaven and earth.

110
00:05:07,980 --> 00:05:09,620
This jewelry is of such poor quality.

111
00:05:09,780 --> 00:05:10,840
I will go reason with them.

112
00:05:12,020 --> 00:05:13,300
It seems to be Chenxin.

113
00:05:13,580 --> 00:05:14,420
Let's go take a look.

114
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:18,740
Sir,

115
00:05:19,940 --> 00:05:21,340
I bought accessories from your shop.

116
00:05:21,740 --> 00:05:23,180
Not only are the designs laughable,

117
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:24,720
but they also broke after two days.

118
00:05:26,420 --> 00:05:28,220
That lady seems to be a maid of Lady Tao.

119
00:05:28,900 --> 00:05:30,020
Do we need to help her?

120
00:05:30,260 --> 00:05:32,020
Wait, let's assess the situation first.

121
00:05:39,810 --> 00:05:40,680
Lady,

122
00:05:40,700 --> 00:05:42,740
this is clearly due to your improper wearing.

123
00:05:42,900 --> 00:05:44,380
It's obviously your poor quality.

124
00:05:44,620 --> 00:05:45,780
You must give me a refund.

125
00:05:45,940 --> 00:05:47,300
This is a bit unreasonable.

126
00:05:47,700 --> 00:05:48,620
I can't return it.

127
00:05:49,740 --> 00:05:50,780
You are being too much.

128
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:52,460
This is clearly your problem.

129
00:05:52,580 --> 00:05:54,160
You just don't want to give me a refund.

130
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:55,820
You don't want to work here anymore?

131
00:05:56,980 --> 00:05:57,820
Chenxin.

132
00:06:00,820 --> 00:06:01,660
Lady Lu.

133
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:03,790
It's been a while since we last met.

134
00:06:03,900 --> 00:06:04,940
How is Lady Tao?

135
00:06:07,380 --> 00:06:08,540
She is very good.

136
00:06:08,700 --> 00:06:09,980
Thank you for your concern.

137
00:06:11,340 --> 00:06:13,380
May I take a look at this hairpin?

138
00:06:51,820 --> 00:06:52,660
Take a look.

139
00:06:52,800 --> 00:06:54,330
How about changing the hairpin to this?

140
00:06:56,940 --> 00:06:57,780
Great!

141
00:06:57,980 --> 00:06:59,080
The craftsmanship is simple.

142
00:06:59,100 --> 00:07:00,500
The style has become more chic.

143
00:07:01,180 --> 00:07:02,800
Originally, there were too many pearls

144
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,880
surrounding the coral stone.

145
00:07:03,940 --> 00:07:05,700
By replacing a few with tassels,

146
00:07:06,140 --> 00:07:08,000
it enhances the brilliance of the coral stone

147
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,750
while retaining the liveliness of the pearls.

148
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:10,580
Elegant and unique.

149
00:07:14,580 --> 00:07:16,020
It's indeed unique.

150
00:07:16,140 --> 00:07:16,980
Don't worry, lady.

151
00:07:16,990 --> 00:07:18,030
According to this pattern,

152
00:07:18,170 --> 00:07:19,290
I will definitely improve it.

153
00:07:19,940 --> 00:07:21,220
I think it looks great too.

154
00:07:21,380 --> 00:07:22,580
Then make it first.

155
00:07:22,860 --> 00:07:23,700
No problem.

156
00:07:23,900 --> 00:07:25,540
In a few days, you can come to pick it up.

157
00:07:28,780 --> 00:07:30,260
Thank you very much.

158
00:07:30,460 --> 00:07:31,740
But I have to hurry back.

159
00:07:31,740 --> 00:07:32,730
I'll take my leave first.

160
00:07:43,740 --> 00:07:44,980
I didn't expect you to have

161
00:07:45,380 --> 00:07:47,020
such a remarkable talent for jewelry.

162
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:49,180
I don't know why.

163
00:07:49,340 --> 00:07:51,340
When I saw it, I felt I could improve it.

164
00:07:51,620 --> 00:07:52,860
I didn't expect it to be decent.

165
00:07:53,300 --> 00:07:54,380
It's more than just decent.

166
00:07:54,580 --> 00:07:55,420
In my opinion,

167
00:07:55,430 --> 00:07:57,090
you're not inferior to a skilled craftsman.

168
00:07:57,660 --> 00:07:58,940
You are flattering me.

169
00:07:59,660 --> 00:08:01,260
With your perspective,

170
00:08:01,380 --> 00:08:02,980
can I open a jewelry shop?

171
00:08:04,100 --> 00:08:04,980
I dare say

172
00:08:05,860 --> 00:08:06,980
it will surely be popular.

173
00:08:09,260 --> 00:08:10,100
See?

174
00:08:10,580 --> 00:08:12,900
The business you long for is right here.

175
00:08:13,780 --> 00:08:14,620
Good fate

176
00:08:14,900 --> 00:08:15,940
always comes unexpectedly.

177
00:08:19,020 --> 00:08:21,060
The river cruise is also a marvel.

178
00:08:21,300 --> 00:08:22,420
Do you want to experience it?

179
00:08:23,820 --> 00:08:24,660
Let's go.

180
00:08:28,380 --> 00:08:29,700
(Mingli Hall)

181
00:08:30,740 --> 00:08:32,700
(Yang Zishu)

182
00:08:32,740 --> 00:08:33,580
Mr. Yang.

183
00:08:36,220 --> 00:08:37,060
Mr. Yang.

184
00:08:37,300 --> 00:08:38,140
Mr. Yang.

185
00:08:41,260 --> 00:08:43,660
I smell the stench of poverty from far away.

186
00:08:44,980 --> 00:08:45,820
Open the door.

187
00:08:49,980 --> 00:08:50,820
Ignore me?

188
00:08:51,260 --> 00:08:53,020
Yang Zishu is bullying a newcomer again.

189
00:08:53,380 --> 00:08:55,220
I heard Mr. Lu has no background.

190
00:08:55,580 --> 00:08:57,140
Looks like he's going to suffer now.

191
00:08:57,580 --> 00:08:58,420
Has Mr. Song arrived?

192
00:08:58,860 --> 00:09:01,340
I think only he can save this guy.

193
00:09:01,940 --> 00:09:03,260
Do you know who my father is?

194
00:09:04,100 --> 00:09:05,540
My father is a sixth-rank official.

195
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:19,310
He was dragged in.

196
00:09:21,900 --> 00:09:22,740
Ouch!

197
00:09:22,940 --> 00:09:23,780
See?

198
00:09:23,980 --> 00:09:25,940
Lu Chang is probably in great danger.

199
00:09:26,100 --> 00:09:26,940
Yeah, that's right.

200
00:09:27,460 --> 00:09:28,700
Listening to this scream,

201
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,660
it is not optimistic.

202
00:09:29,660 --> 00:09:31,020
How dare he offend Yang Zishu!

203
00:09:31,020 --> 00:09:32,700
- Yeah.
- Who dares to offend him?

204
00:09:33,260 --> 00:09:34,180
What's going on?

205
00:09:37,100 --> 00:09:38,340
You guys, from now on,

206
00:09:38,340 --> 00:09:39,360
- It's Mr. Lu.
- Mr. Lu.

207
00:09:40,060 --> 00:09:40,900
This person

208
00:09:41,060 --> 00:09:42,220
is Mr. Lu, my buddy.

209
00:09:45,020 --> 00:09:46,980
Be more respectful, got that?

210
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:47,980
Could this guy

211
00:09:47,980 --> 00:09:48,820
cast a spell

212
00:09:48,820 --> 00:09:49,980
on Yang Zishu?

213
00:09:49,980 --> 00:09:50,820
It shouldn't be.

214
00:09:50,910 --> 00:09:51,780
Mr. Lu.

215
00:09:51,900 --> 00:09:52,740
Mr. Song.

216
00:09:53,540 --> 00:09:54,380
Nice to see you.

217
00:09:57,740 --> 00:09:59,340
