218
00:10:00,180 --> 00:10:01,420
I truly apologize.

219
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:06,960
Yang Zishu has always bullied newcomers.

220
00:10:07,460 --> 00:10:08,620
How did you subdue him?

221
00:10:09,700 --> 00:10:11,360
I said I could teach him to fight crickets.

222
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:13,240
Thanks to the headmaster's reminder,

223
00:10:13,940 --> 00:10:15,500
I realized he has this hobby.

224
00:10:16,100 --> 00:10:18,060
You actually have such a refined taste.

225
00:10:18,860 --> 00:10:20,140
Mr. Song, don't joke around.

226
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,150
I just played around in the countryside

227
00:10:22,150 --> 00:10:23,340
during childhood.

228
00:10:23,900 --> 00:10:24,880
But it's more than enough

229
00:10:25,340 --> 00:10:26,300
to deal with him.

230
00:10:27,060 --> 00:10:27,900
With you around,

231
00:10:28,180 --> 00:10:30,500
I am finally not bored in this academy.

232
00:10:32,020 --> 00:10:34,140
Why didn't I see you in class before?

233
00:10:34,580 --> 00:10:35,420
I...

234
00:10:35,540 --> 00:10:37,980
I went to purchase some writing materials.

235
00:10:38,540 --> 00:10:39,820
I ran into your sister before.

236
00:10:40,300 --> 00:10:42,180
She said she's very fond of the scenery here.

237
00:10:42,660 --> 00:10:44,540
I'll take you around the city another day

238
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:46,020
and show me proper hospitality.

239
00:10:46,020 --> 00:10:47,580
(Mingde Pavilion)

240
00:10:47,580 --> 00:10:48,590
Schoolwork is complicated.

241
00:10:48,860 --> 00:10:49,780
How dare I trouble you

242
00:10:50,020 --> 00:10:51,420
to take time out to accompany us?

243
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:52,880
Mr. Lu, don't be polite with me.

244
00:10:53,420 --> 00:10:57,180
(Baiyu Shop)

245
00:10:57,460 --> 00:10:59,500
(For transfer)
If I want to open a jewelry shop,

246
00:11:00,020 --> 00:11:02,100
